# Cooking Master - WordPress Theme

## 🔗 Live Demo
https://www.wpthemesdemo.com/cooking-master/

---

## 📌 Overview
Cooking Master is a custom WordPress theme designed for food bloggers, chefs, restaurants, and cooking enthusiasts.

The theme focuses on presenting recipes, blogs, and food content in a visually appealing and user-friendly way.

Ideal for:
- Food bloggers
- Recipe websites
- Chefs & culinary experts
- Restaurants and cafes

---

## ✨ Features
- Fully custom WordPress theme (no page builder dependency)
- Clean and modern UI design
- Fully responsive layout (mobile, tablet, desktop)
- Recipe and blog-friendly layout
- Image-focused design for food presentation
- SEO-friendly structure
- Fast loading and optimized performance
- Cross-browser compatibility

